  <input type="submit" value="_(Reload gateway)_">
  </form>
<blockquote class="inline_help">_(Native Unraid controls for the running gateway. Reload reconciles the gateway config and refreshes upstream discovery without embedding the separate labby web UI.)_</blockquote>

<form markdown="1" method="post">
<input type="hidden" name="labby_gateway_add" value="1">

